{"tid":581450,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【100毛上市】毛記通過上市聆訊 月內啟動招股籌逾億","createTime":"2018-03-05T10:58:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-05T15:12:39.000Z","uid":43072,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1fb2c2f168a0a64737bbfcee6f53db769ee71be2","tid":581450,"uid":43072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"市場消息指，《黑紙》、《100毛》及毛記電視母公司「毛記葵涌」上周已通過上市聆訊，將於本月內啟動招股程序，料集資逾1億元。<br />\n<br />\n本報記者曾就此致電查詢，毛記創辦人之一林日曦表示忙於拍攝，未能接受訪問。<br />\n<br />\n毛記去年7月26日上傳初步申請文件，惟事隔半年後失效，毛記於1月29日重新遞交，不足兩個月即獲批准上市。<br />\n<br />\n毛記2010年成立，初期以「黑紙」、「100毛」等印刷業務起家，2016年起為客戶提供一站式廣告方案的數碼媒體服務。毛記現時有三大業務，包括數碼媒體服務、印刷媒體服務、活動策劃及藝人管理。截至去年3月底止，毛記全年收入高達9,522.8萬元，按年升73.6%；期內賺3,626.3萬元，按年升61.9%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180305/57907838\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907838&d=EdwsfXnqx%2BIl7aQGhwu2pm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=1cb63787\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180305%2F57907838&h=e2a26ae8\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20180305/57907838</a>"},{"pid":"c4984b5b8dc0795d8e89c5f0e08dca0b833b550f","tid":581450,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"一定勁過 14年既Magnum<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd99c5f253f58c27d6dac592330a317786df0f88","tid":581450,"uid":158613,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:04:47.000Z","msg":"變質了"},{"pid":"361d1639552c30be9e6afb0f54f07032db2aa6ee","tid":581450,"uid":43072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-05T11:05:24.000Z","msg":"保薦人咩背景<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a3e42d27f4066fdf73f8682037feffc009a870","tid":58145